{"tid":640634,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［轉行］請教各位工程巴打","createTime":"2018-04-24T11:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T14:31:56.000Z","uid":9939,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6af7125a2d1c677b6a0896ab02e99cc299136045","tid":640634,"uid":9939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:56:12.000Z","msg":"小弟年30做開銀行搵廿鬆啲，做耐左都肯定唔會點發展到落去。 屋企人做開工程，想襯自己仲未算老行得走得想試下做工程<br />\n<br />\n咁我本身讀bba對工程零認識，想注重向水喉果方面發展，請問熟行情既工程巴指教下條路應該點行，坊間好似唔覺有講工程既書買，係咪應該去職訓局讀啲短期課程考下牌再向水喉匠條路行呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者可以係邊到吸下知識，感謝賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d170f11c67d82b3de97f4d7e14360a38fc8eb7","tid":640634,"uid":61600,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:00:17.000Z","msg":"轉咩都好 唔好轉工程"},{"pid":"f22355e4b4b648df89c8f3074c571ab7b21a6354","tid":640634,"uid":9939,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e8d170f11c67d82b3de97f4d7e14360a38fc8eb7","tid":640634,"uid":61600,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:00:17.000Z","msg":"轉咩都好 唔好轉工程"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:03:12.000Z","msg":"屋企人做開，係判頭我想繼承衣缽，而且呢行又穩定，有冇咩原因個個都話唔好入？"},{"pid":"5350d42b971c227e8c07e5cfd953c6737037c24d","tid":640634,"uid":123711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:05:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f41fc6a4add1a9c6d819809d9e776cce1dfac21","tid":640634,"uid":44504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:05:43.000Z","msg":"有銀行唔做做地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13125609810b1490bea9da8d91599c3792f1e997","tid":640634,"uid":9939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f41fc6a4add1a9c6d819809d9e776cce1dfac21","tid":640634,"uid":44504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:05:43.000Z","msg":"有銀行唔做做地盤<img src=